Primers and samples

hist(qpcr$CT, main = "CT values")

#Plot CT values for samples
ggplot(qpcr, aes(Sample, CT)) +
  geom_boxplot() +

  ggtitle("CT values per sample")

ggplot(qpcr, aes(Gene, CT)) +
